snippet.title: Announcing the Convetion Hotel
snippet.place: SOFITEL MUNICH BAYERPOST IN MUNICH, GERMANY
snippet.placeDesc: We are thrilled to announce the hotel for the 2019 Global Convention. We will be staying at the Sofitel Munich Bayerpost Hotel in the heart of the city. Sofitel hotels are known to draw inspiration from the local traditions and authentic culture of each location. As a former Bavarian Royal Post Office, the Sofitel Munich Bayerpost is an ideal location for sophisticated business and exciting adventures. We look forward to seeing you there!
